label: SDTM Controlled Terminology Package 48 Effective 2021-12-17
name: SDTM CT 2021-12-17
source: SDTM Controlled Terminology developed by the CDISC Terminology Team in collaboration with the National Cancer Institute's Enterprise Vocabulary Services (EVS)
